				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6912193/scp-3896#post-3912814</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 16 Aug 2018 01:02:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Genshed</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2643500</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was a little on the fence about Gorzugaal, but then I realized that it was a connection to Napoleon Bonyparts. There's an eldritch abomination in town, and it's got an agenda.</p> <p>The implication that death is no release is disturbingly close to some of the Factory SCPs, and the chipper attitude of the griddle jockeys just makes it more queasy-making. Whatever Big G is, it's not good news.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
